		</h3>
		<p>Sii with Dollar UK organise a great charity undertaking - BiSIIcle Challenge – Do IT For IT. The main task for Sii & Dollar employees is to cover simultaneously 1163,4 miles on stationary bikes. Bisiicles are located in Dolar & Sii  Gdansk Branch offices. During 3 months Dollar and Sii teams will travel virtually from Gdansk to Nottingham on bikes and other way round. In BiSiicle Challenge take part - in both teams (max 4 members) and individuals. Team’s locations are available on Google Maps – you can track participants’ progresses whenever you want thanks to this app. Covering a total distance Gdansk-Nottinhgam and Nottingham-Gdansk =  funds for charity.!</p>
