		<p>The Challenge has already started on September 26th  and plan to end at the end of the year. We have 9 Exercise Bikes (2 in Bicester and 4 in Nottingham and 3 in Gdansk) and ALL mileage must be done on the provided bikes. The idea being that time before work, during work (if on a call etc.), lunchtimes, other breaks and after work will be utilised to complete target miles. Participants are not be able to book time on the bikes but instead will be on a first come basis of availability.</p>
